OL,7,FChildren with special educational
OL,8,Fneeds are to be offered free NHS
OL,9,Fhearing, dental and eyesight checks.
OL,11,FThe checks will be rolled out in
OL,12,Fresidential special schools and
OL,13,Fcolleges from next year.
OL,15,FAutistic children and those living
OL,16,Fwith learning disabilities are more
OL,17,Flikely to experience hearing, eyesight
OL,18,Fand dental problems than their peers.
