OL,3,CEye and ear checks to be offered to
OL,4,Cthousands of children in special
OL,5,Cschools
OL,7,FNHS sensory checks were piloted by the
OL,8,FGovernment in 2022 and 2023 and the
OL,9,Fnew programme is expected to reach
OL,10,Faround 18,000 students.
OL,12,FAll staff carrying out the sensory
OL,13,Fchecks will be appropriately qualified
OL,14,Fand trained.
OL,16,FNational Learning Disability and
OL,17,FAutism Director at NHS England Tom
OL,18,FCahill said the new checks would
OL,19,Fensure any issues are identified
OL,20,Fpromptly.
