OL,4,Cthousands of children in special
OL,5,Cschools
OL,7,F"Mainstream services can sometimes
OL,8,Fstruggle to meet the needs of autistic
OL,9,Fchildren and young people, or those
OL,10,Fwith a profound learning disability,
OL,11,Fso these new sensory checks in
OL,12,Fresidential special schools will
OL,13,Fprovide the support they need," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
