OL,3,CEye and ear checks to be offered to
OL,4,Cthousands of children in special
OL,5,Cschools
OL,7,FMinister of State for Care, Stephen
OL,8,FKinnock said the checkups would help
OL,9,Ftackle health inequality and give
OL,10,Faccess to support faster.
OL,12,F"I am pleased we will be able to
OL,13,Fsupport vital sensory checks for all
OL,14,Fpupils in special educational
OL,15,Fsettings, in a comfortable and known
OL,16,Fenvironment for them," he said.
OL,18,F"These checks will enable health
OL,19,Fissues in around 18,000 children and
OL,20,Fyoung people to be identified more
OL,21,Fpromptly."
